### Create default time slots for therapist
POST http://localhost:8000/api/therapists/1/slots
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2024-03-01"
}

### Create custom time slots for therapist
POST http://localhost:8000/api/therapists/1/slots
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2024-03-02",
  "slots": [
    {"start": "09:00", "end": "11:00"},
    {"start": "13:00", "end": "15:00"}
  ]
}

### Get time slots for therapist on specific date
GET http://localhost:8000/api/therapists/1/slots/2024-03-01

### Update a time slot
PATCH http://localhost:8000/api/slots/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "is_booked": true
}

### Delete a time slot
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/slots/1

### Get available slots in date range
GET http://localhost:8000/api/therapists/1/available?startDate=2024-03-01&endDate=2024-03-31